{
  "stem": "4272.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't think I could-- I would have the guts anymore now, but then, somehow, I did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't realize what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they-- they took me back to the cell and again interrogated me and again interrogated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once, on the way back from interrogation, I was going to my cell, and a man was sitting there-- a German-- and he said oh, Smiechowska, aus Juden.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he thought he'll catch me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When he'll say aus Juden, I will turn around and try to defend myself, which means I do speak German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Aus-- aus Juden, means that you come from Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I pretended that I didn't even hear him, and I went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was right after Christmas, so there was-- they could look in through the-- what do you call that hole in the doors that you can look in and out?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you call those?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Peepholes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a peephole into the cell, and I didn't know, but they were watching me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was singing the Christmas songs with the other women that were arrested.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they could not-- not that they had to prove much, so another Polish woman would be killed, so what?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Instead of leaving a Jew alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I don't know why that they just didn't do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the tricks that they use.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took me out to the-- to the office, and they said they would like me to clean it up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I cleaned it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I moved everything and I dusted everything and I washed the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said no, she's not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Out of the question.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
